criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Age 20-40

          -  intact sight / corrected sight

          -  Hebrew as mother tongue

          -  Intact comprehension

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Active neurologic or psychiatric diagnosis.

          -  If Had been treated with HBOT for any other reason prior to their inclusion;

          -  Chest pathology ;

          -  Inner ear disease;

          -  Claustrophobia;
